data.name: SqlInsertCommand1.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO [Movie] ([DVD_Id], [Title], [Director], [Actor1], [Actor2], [Language], [Rating], [Genre], [Release_year], [Duration], [Poster]) VALUES (@DVD_Id, @Title, @Director, @Actor1, @Actor2, @Language, @Rating, @Genre, @Release_year, @Duration, @Poster); SELECT Movie_Id, DVD_Id, Title, Director, Actor1, Actor2, Language, Rating, Genre, Release_year, Duration, Poster FROM Movie WHERE (Movie_Id = SCOPE_IDENTITY())

data.name: SqlUpdateCommand1.CommandText
